<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="75400000t" end="98600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">(還能爭取多少自由)</p>
<p begin="182200000t" end="221000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">「約定的夢幻島」</p>
<p begin="254200000t" end="263000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">(Fire)</p>
<p begin="269400000t" end="291800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">(該我出場了　率先上陣)</p>
<p begin="292600000t" end="316200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(在知道何謂失敗之前)</p>
<p begin="317000000t" end="345000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(先找到導火線)</p>
<p begin="345800000t" end="357400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="358200000t" end="387400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(沒有神明可崇拜　也沒有星星)</p>
<p begin="388200000t" end="413400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(但是從沒放棄祈求)</p>
<p begin="414200000t" end="441000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(因害怕後悔而停滯的腳步)</p>
<p begin="441800000t" end="451800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="452600000t" end="500200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(想忘記的正是無法忘掉的事)</p>
<p begin="501000000t" end="547000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(通往天堂之路始於地獄)</p>
<p begin="547800000t" end="594600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(一點火花化為熊熊烈火)</p>
<p begin="595400000t" end="628200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(緊張不安地不斷追趕)</p>
<p begin="629000000t" end="652600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(奔往未來)</p>
<p begin="653400000t" end="675000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">(儘管只是數厘米)</p>
<p begin="675800000t" end="698600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">(也要朝著願望中的目的地)</p>
<p begin="699400000t" end="722200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="750200000t" end="796600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">(為內心贖罪　勸自己放棄)</p>
<p begin="797400000t" end="817800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">(這樣將來還能說甚麼)</p>
<p begin="844200000t" end="865800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="1109400000t" end="1130200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">你在這裡的生活過得好嗎</p>
<p begin="1131000000t" end="1141800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">我過得很好</p>
<p begin="1142600000t" end="1158600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">這間孤兒院實在太好了</p>
<p begin="1159400000t" end="1183400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">小朋友都很優秀，還很乖</p>
<p begin="1184200000t" end="1211800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">是嗎？你最近都有聽我吩咐</p>
<p begin="1212600000t" end="1223400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">而且做事又認真</p>
<p begin="1224200000t" end="1259000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">真的很聽話　　是</p>
<p begin="1264600000t" end="1287800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">你努力想跟小朋友打成一片</p>
<p begin="1288600000t" end="1312200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">而且還盡全力跟他們玩捉迷藏</p>
<p begin="1313000000t" end="1325000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">因為你的言談舉止</p>
<p begin="1325800000t" end="1339800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">我本來也有擔心過</p>
<p begin="1340600000t" end="1354200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">但是看來沒甚麼問題</p>
<p begin="1368600000t" end="1383400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">你是一份保險</p>
<p begin="1384200000t" end="1393800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">你在這裡的作用</p>
<p begin="1394600000t" end="1412200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">就是更全面地保護商品</p>
<p begin="1413000000t" end="1430600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我只不過是為了慎重起見</p>
<p begin="1431400000t" end="1443400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">才會叫你來</p>
<p begin="1452200000t" end="1473400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">所以你並不需要知道</p>
<p begin="1474200000t" end="1501000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">到底是哪個小朋友知道了秘密</p>
<p begin="1501800000t" end="1531400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">你只要假裝聽我的話，好好工作</p>
<p begin="1532200000t" end="1557000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">對於你掌握我的弱點這件事</p>
<p begin="1557800000t" end="1575400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">你大聲地一笑置之就可以了</p>
<p begin="1581400000t" end="1594200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">哪有這樣的事</p>
<p begin="1595000000t" end="1622200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">你不過是我的一隻棋子</p>
<p begin="1623000000t" end="1640200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">所以你不應該做其他的事</p>
<p begin="1669400000t" end="1691000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">只要乖乖聽我的話</p>
<p begin="1733800000t" end="1765400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">我遲早也一定讓你做孤兒院的媽媽</p>
<p begin="1766200000t" end="1779000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">我可以向你保證</p>
<p begin="1824600000t" end="1848200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">我能看出你是一個聰明的女人</p>
<p begin="1849000000t" end="1872600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">希望你以後不要再行差踏錯</p>
<p begin="2223800000t" end="2242600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">那個女人…</p>
<p begin="2292200000t" end="2327400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">你儘管看著吧，我一定會對付你</p>
<p begin="2328200000t" end="2340600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">令你的地位不保</p>
<p begin="2433400000t" end="2476200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">然後我就會成為媽媽</p>
<p begin="2525800000t" end="2531400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="2539000000t" end="2547800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">從今天開始</p>
<p begin="2548600000t" end="2564590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">我們分成小隊玩捉迷藏</p>
<p begin="2565400000t" end="2575790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">分成小隊？</p>
<p begin="2576600000t" end="2594590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">如果繼續像現在這樣單獨逃走</p>
<p begin="2595400000t" end="2608990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">幾乎是必死無疑</p>
<p begin="2609800000t" end="2622600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">阿雷</p>
<p begin="2623400000t" end="2637000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">不過接受訓練之後</p>
<p begin="2637800000t" end="2652200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">大家的身手都不錯</p>
<p begin="2653000000t" end="2671400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">只要我們不要單獨行動就可以了</p>
<p begin="2675800000t" end="2686600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">所以我們現在要組隊</p>
<p begin="2687400000t" end="2703400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">一起離開這裡</p>
<p begin="2704200000t" end="2731400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">這次捉迷藏的形式更接近實戰</p>
<p begin="2732200000t" end="2744200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">接近實戰…</p>
<p begin="2745000000t" end="2760200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">我還有一個提議想說</p>
<p begin="2772600000t" end="2791000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">不如拉攏阿唐和吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="2791800000t" end="2805000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">將實情告訴他們</p>
<p begin="2805800000t" end="2819800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">叫他們負責帶領小隊</p>
<p begin="2825400000t" end="2844600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">如果他們是媽媽的情報來源</p>
<p begin="2845400000t" end="2852200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">那怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="2855800000t" end="2869800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">這也沒問題</p>
<p begin="2870600000t" end="2891000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">我們想查出他們是否情報來源</p>
<p begin="2891800000t" end="2901800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">跟拉攏他們</p>
<p begin="2902600000t" end="2919000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">這兩件事可以同時進行</p>
<p begin="2929000000t" end="2948200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">而且我已經做好準備</p>
<p begin="2957800000t" end="2963800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="2973400000t" end="3001400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">我現在會說出100種不同的隊形</p>
<p begin="3002200000t" end="3012600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">你要全部都記住</p>
<p begin="3017800000t" end="3035000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">聽你說一次就要記住？</p>
<p begin="3035800000t" end="3045800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">你做不到嗎</p>
<p begin="3065000000t" end="3075800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">這很容易</p>
<p begin="3140200000t" end="3170200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">大家在接下來的10分鐘儘量逃走</p>
<p begin="3176200000t" end="3182600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">開始</p>
<p begin="3215800000t" end="3236600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">大家記得要跟著我</p>
<p begin="3237400000t" end="3255400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">不要讓阿雷捉到，要嚇他一跳</p>
<p begin="3273000000t" end="3285400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">就這樣做吧</p>
<p begin="3705000000t" end="3721400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">很好玩</p>
<p begin="3722200000t" end="3747000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">菲爾，你這次真的玩得很棒</p>
<p begin="3747800000t" end="3766200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">這次這種玩法很好玩</p>
<p begin="3767000000t" end="3786200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">下次我也要負責做隊長</p>
<p begin="3787000000t" end="3807000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">不過我們還是先休息一會吧</p>
<p begin="3849400000t" end="3864200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">分小隊玩捉迷藏這個辦法</p>
<p begin="3865000000t" end="3877400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">似乎行得通</p>
<p begin="3902600000t" end="3923000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">菲爾的分數是多少</p>
<p begin="3944600000t" end="3959800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">菲爾的分數是…</p>
<p begin="3965000000t" end="3977000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">他最近的平均分</p>
<p begin="3977800000t" end="3999400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">好像大約是203多一點</p>
<p begin="4000200000t" end="4009400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">很高分</p>
<p begin="4012600000t" end="4033800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">跟修女玩捉迷藏時是這樣</p>
<p begin="4034600000t" end="4043400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">這次也是這樣</p>
<p begin="4049000000t" end="4075000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">菲爾每次都是玩到最後才被人捉到</p>
<p begin="4087800000t" end="4125000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">而且他經常跟雪莉一起去找你們</p>
<p begin="4189400000t" end="4199000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">不要再說了</p>
<p begin="4199800000t" end="4219800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">我始終還是不想去懷疑其他人</p>
<p begin="4220600000t" end="4235800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">傻丫頭，就算不想</p>
<p begin="4236600000t" end="4256200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">也要多些徹底去懷疑其他人</p>
<p begin="4257000000t" end="4275400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">這件事關乎我們的生死</p>
<p begin="4389000000t" end="4397400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">對了，阿雷</p>
<p begin="4403800000t" end="4412200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">那次之後</p>
<p begin="4413000000t" end="4436600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">發信器破壞方法的研究順利嗎</p>
<p begin="4437400000t" end="4457800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">大約還要多久才可以完成</p>
<p begin="4458600000t" end="4481800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">讓我想想，10日就夠了</p>
<p begin="4489000000t" end="4507800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">那就10日之後實行計劃</p>
<p begin="4521800000t" end="4542200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">我們的逃走計劃就在10日之後</p>
<p begin="4543000000t" end="4553800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">11月8日實行</p>
<p begin="4579400000t" end="4600200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">慢著，這樣不會太急嗎</p>
<p begin="4601000000t" end="4611000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">雖然沒甚麼所謂</p>
<p begin="4611800000t" end="4626200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">當然有所謂</p>
<p begin="4627000000t" end="4647800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">柯妮出欄到現在過了兩個星期</p>
<p begin="4648600000t" end="4671000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">我們明知出欄週期最短是兩個月</p>
<p begin="4671800000t" end="4692600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">所以現在還有一個半月的時間</p>
<p begin="4693400000t" end="4703400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">我們不是說好了</p>
<p begin="4704200000t" end="4728600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">要在這段時間內做好充分準備嗎</p>
<p begin="4737800000t" end="4757000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">媽媽也會像阿雷這樣想</p>
<p begin="4757800000t" end="4773800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">為了令我們有這種想法</p>
<p begin="4774600000t" end="4783800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">而在控制我們</p>
<p begin="4793800000t" end="4810600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">所以我們也要將計就計</p>
<p begin="4829400000t" end="4840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">如果因為太著急行動</p>
<p begin="4841400000t" end="4856600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">最後失敗了怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="4857400000t" end="4880600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">我們無論如何都要在冬天前逃走</p>
<p begin="4887400000t" end="4903800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">當成功破壞發信器之後</p>
<p begin="4904600000t" end="4924600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">立即以最快速度實行逃走計劃</p>
<p begin="4929800000t" end="4942200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">要在10日之內</p>
<p begin="4943000000t" end="4960200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">準備好所有計劃內需要的東西嗎</p>
<p begin="4995000000t" end="5025800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">今晚就向阿唐和吉爾妲說出實情</p>
<p begin="5568600000t" end="5591400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">你們記著要配合我</p>
<p begin="5643000000t" end="5657800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">你有甚麼要說</p>
<p begin="5703800000t" end="5723000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">你說人口販賣？</p>
<p begin="5781000000t" end="5809800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">之前被送走的那些兄弟姐妹</p>
<p begin="5810600000t" end="5823400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">全部都賣了給壞人</p>
<p begin="5882600000t" end="5907800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">沒可能，根本就沒可能</p>
<p begin="5908600000t" end="5929000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">這裡不只有圍牆，還有門</p>
<p begin="5929800000t" end="5947000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">而且那些離開了的兄弟姐妹</p>
<p begin="5947800000t" end="5967000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">一封信都沒有寄回來</p>
<p begin="5967800000t" end="5981000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">你還想騙我？</p>
<p begin="5981800000t" end="5999000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">然後呢？笑點是甚麼</p>
<p begin="5999800000t" end="6015400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">這個到底是甚麼遊戲</p>
<p begin="6077800000t" end="6094600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">不要跟我說是真的</p>
<p begin="6100600000t" end="6107800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">是真的</p>
<p begin="6129000000t" end="6145800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">等等，那麼媽媽呢</p>
<p begin="6158600000t" end="6201800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">媽媽一直在將我們賣給壞人</p>
<p begin="6215000000t" end="6222200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">這麼溫柔的媽媽</p>
<p begin="6223000000t" end="6238600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">怎麼可能做出這樣的事</p>
<p begin="6239400000t" end="6265000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">收回你的話，艾瑪　　阿唐</p>
<p begin="6285800000t" end="6304600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">最喜歡孤兒院</p>
<p begin="6305400000t" end="6327000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">和最喜歡媽媽的艾瑪</p>
<p begin="6333400000t" end="6353000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">沒可能會說這種謊言</p>
<p begin="6379400000t" end="6388600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">吉爾妲…</p>
<p begin="6395800000t" end="6432200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">而且我一直覺得有件事很奇怪</p>
<p begin="6435000000t" end="6453400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">就是柯妮離開那天</p>
<p begin="6462600000t" end="6490600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">艾瑪和諾曼曾經一起去過門那邊</p>
<p begin="6491400000t" end="6501800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">去過門那邊？</p>
<p begin="6530200000t" end="6541000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">如果是平時的話</p>
<p begin="6541800000t" end="6564600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">他們就算違反了規則</p>
<p begin="6565400000t" end="6581400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">都會立即誠實認錯</p>
<p begin="6582200000t" end="6595000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">然後變回平時那樣</p>
<p begin="6595800000t" end="6611800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">但是他們這次沒有這樣做</p>
<p begin="6640200000t" end="6671400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">艾瑪，她對這件事非常認真</p>
<p begin="6672200000t" end="6695800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">而我又越來越沒辦法開口問她</p>
<p begin="6758200000t" end="6785400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">對不起…吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="6786200000t" end="6799400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">竟然令你這麼擔心</p>
<p begin="6812600000t" end="6825400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">艾瑪，你有否…</p>
<p begin="6835800000t" end="6861000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">看到柯妮被賣給那個…</p>
<p begin="6862200000t" end="6881800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">那個壞人是怎樣的</p>
<p begin="6897000000t" end="6902600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">有</p>
<p begin="6915800000t" end="6931000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">但是我們趕不及</p>
<p begin="6931800000t" end="6954600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">那麼柯妮呢？她現在怎樣</p>
<p begin="6955400000t" end="6963000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">不知道</p>
<p begin="6997800000t" end="7023800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">怎麼會這樣…</p>
<p begin="7045000000t" end="7067800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">雖然不知道是否算是證據</p>
<p begin="7068600000t" end="7079000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">但是這張紙</p>
<p begin="7079800000t" end="7095000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">寫了這幾天阿雷和艾瑪</p>
<p begin="7095800000t" end="7117000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">調查過各兄弟姐妹的分數</p>
<p begin="7117800000t" end="7130600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">你說分數嗎…</p>
<p begin="7149800000t" end="7177400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">離開了的小朋友都是六歲以上</p>
<p begin="7178200000t" end="7191400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">然後從低至高的分數</p>
<p begin="7192200000t" end="7217000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">順序給人領養，很奇怪吧</p>
<p begin="7223400000t" end="7246600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">柯妮的分數真的挺低</p>
<p begin="7247400000t" end="7261400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">阿豪和賽蒂也是</p>
<p begin="7267400000t" end="7290600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">跟諾曼所說的一樣</p>
<p begin="7291400000t" end="7309800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">阿唐、吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="7310600000t" end="7328200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">我們一起逃走</p>
<p begin="7329000000t" end="7346600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">一起想辦法去救柯妮他們</p>
<p begin="7349800000t" end="7373000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">全部人一起離開這間孤兒院</p>
<p begin="7380200000t" end="7389000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">幫幫我們</p>
<p begin="7581000000t" end="7606200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">諾曼　　你想問出欄的事？</p>
<p begin="7607000000t" end="7620600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">究竟甚麼叫「不知道」</p>
<p begin="7626600000t" end="7646200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">應該告訴阿唐她死了</p>
<p begin="7647000000t" end="7663800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">為了順利拉攏他們</p>
<p begin="7664600000t" end="7676600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">這樣回答是最好的</p>
<p begin="7677400000t" end="7696600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">如果他們都不是內奸</p>
<p begin="7707000000t" end="7724200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">這種謊言實在太殘酷了</p>
<p begin="7729400000t" end="7743000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">甚麼仍然生存</p>
<p begin="7743800000t" end="7764200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">不要給他們這些不存在的希望</p>
<p begin="7779000000t" end="7805800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">等到何時、怎樣告訴他們真相</p>
<p begin="7811000000t" end="7818600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">你能說出來嗎</p>
<p begin="7827000000t" end="7844200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">將來的事，將來再說</p>
<p begin="7850200000t" end="7874600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">而且還未可以確定他們不是內奸</p>
<p begin="7875400000t" end="7899800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">我會順便設置陷阱　　陷阱？</p>
<p begin="7912600000t" end="7935800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">我會告訴他們繩子藏在哪裡</p>
<p begin="7959000000t" end="7982600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">告訴阿唐，繩子藏在我的床下</p>
<p begin="7983400000t" end="7993800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">告訴吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="7994600000t" end="8010600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">繩子藏在二樓廁所天花板</p>
<p begin="8023800000t" end="8038600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">誰會怎樣行動</p>
<p begin="8039400000t" end="8059400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">情報會怎樣洩漏給媽媽</p>
<p begin="8060200000t" end="8074600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">憑這個陷阱就知道</p>
<p begin="8075400000t" end="8082600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">那麼繩子呢</p>
<p begin="8089400000t" end="8106600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">如果他們都不是內奸</p>
<p begin="8107400000t" end="8127800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">沒有實物的話，情況會變得很複雜</p>
<p begin="8128600000t" end="8145800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">我已經將繩子預備好</p>
<p begin="8160600000t" end="8180600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">原來早就萬事俱備</p>
<p begin="8181400000t" end="8192200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">我說過了</p>
<p begin="8199800000t" end="8217400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">我們要將計就計</p>
<p begin="8252600000t" end="8270200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">別走，等等</p>
<p begin="8289400000t" end="8305400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">我覺得好像很久</p>
<p begin="8306200000t" end="8331000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">沒有跟艾瑪這樣兩人聊天</p>
<p begin="8331800000t" end="8361800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">很奇怪吧，明明每天都在一起</p>
<p begin="8389800000t" end="8405800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">我們從今天開始</p>
<p begin="8406600000t" end="8422200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">會一直在一起吧</p>
<p begin="9164000000t" end="9176400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">原來如此</p>
<p begin="9177200000t" end="9200800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">繩子藏了在諾曼的床下</p>
<p begin="9276800000t" end="9298000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">我一直在等你，吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="9505200000t" end="9528000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">來，告訴我，吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="9547600000t" end="9578800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">是之前提過那件事吧</p>
<p begin="9702800000t" end="9721200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">我真的甚麼煩惱都沒有</p>
<p begin="9722000000t" end="9733200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">我知道你因為擔心我</p>
<p begin="9734000000t" end="9749200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">所以好幾次主動關心我</p>
<p begin="9750000000t" end="9764000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">真的很感謝你</p>
<p begin="9764800000t" end="9797200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">是嗎？我真的很擔心你</p>
<p begin="9798000000t" end="9816800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">但是我現在已經沒事了</p>
<p begin="9817600000t" end="9840400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">所以請拜託你，不要再管我的事情</p>
<p begin="9841200000t" end="9852800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">打擾了</p>
<p begin="9889200000t" end="9899200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">原來如此</p>
<p begin="9900000000t" end="9932800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">看來艾瑪已經將所有事情全告訴你</p>
<p begin="9966000000t" end="9988000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">吉爾妲，快些告訴我</p>
<p begin="9988800000t" end="10022400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">你現在是否已經全部清楚了解</p>
<p begin="10097600000t" end="10116800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">真可惜，吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="10117600000t" end="10130800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">我還以為這次有機會</p>
<p begin="10131600000t" end="10151600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">可以跟你成為好朋友</p>
<p begin="10162800000t" end="10188800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">這件事究竟還有誰知道</p>
<p begin="10189600000t" end="10224000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">除了諾曼、阿雷，還有誰</p>
<p begin="10256400000t" end="10279600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">放心，我會特別放過你一個</p>
<p begin="10280400000t" end="10296800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">我們以後好好相處</p>
<p begin="10392800000t" end="10405990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">請你不要這樣</p>
<p begin="10437600000t" end="10459200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">我根本不知道你在說甚麼</p>
<p begin="10460000000t" end="10478800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">我只是跟艾瑪吵架了</p>
<p begin="10479600000t" end="10490400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">但是已經和好如初</p>
<p begin="10491200000t" end="10508000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">所以現在甚麼事也沒有</p>
<p begin="10537200000t" end="10544800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">是嗎</p>
<p begin="10545600000t" end="10570800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">看來是我誤會了，對不起</p>
<p begin="10606000000t" end="10629200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">如果你覺得艾瑪在說謊</p>
<p begin="10630000000t" end="10652800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">到時你就再來找我，告訴我</p>
<p begin="10682000000t" end="10695600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">再見，吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="10812000000t" end="10830400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">艾瑪　　吉爾妲</p>
<p begin="10945200000t" end="10962000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">即使吉爾妲不行</p>
<p begin="10969600000t" end="10990000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">我也不會這麼容易放棄</p>
<p begin="11020000000t" end="11044400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">托馬大人出場</p>
<p begin="11060400000t" end="11080400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">這樣會有問題嗎</p>
<p begin="11081200000t" end="11088400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">我們走吧</p>
<p begin="11094400000t" end="11106000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">媽媽在盯著</p>
<p begin="11162000000t" end="11181600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">根據艾瑪留意到的結果</p>
<p begin="11182400000t" end="11197600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">吉爾妲沒有可疑的地方</p>
<p begin="11210800000t" end="11241600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">阿雷，你覺得內奸為甚麼會做內奸</p>
<p begin="11252800000t" end="11260800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">這當然是因為</p>
<p begin="11261600000t" end="11284000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">做內奸可以得到相應的好處</p>
<p begin="11284800000t" end="11306000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">而好處可能是可以避免出欄</p>
<p begin="11306800000t" end="11319200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">長大成人之類的事</p>
<p begin="11342000000t" end="11359200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">是生命安全的保證？</p>
<p begin="11426800000t" end="11441600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">原來如此</p>
<p begin="11442400000t" end="11468800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">這個其實是為了逃走而做的訓練</p>
<p begin="11516000000t" end="11550000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">1、2、3</p>
<p begin="11550800000t" end="11578800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">艾瑪，你有空嗎</p>
<p begin="11594400000t" end="11614400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">我想聽聽你有甚麼想法</p>
<p begin="11625600000t" end="11644000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">如果有一個小朋友</p>
<p begin="11644800000t" end="11660000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">自願成為鬼的手下</p>
<p begin="11666000000t" end="11680000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">只要他肯做內奸</p>
<p begin="11680800000t" end="11703600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">就可以得到生命安全的保證的話</p>
<p begin="11711200000t" end="11727200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">即是說只要願意做內奸</p>
<p begin="11728000000t" end="11750800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">就不會被送出欄，可以生存下來？</p>
<p begin="11751600000t" end="11790800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">是，你會留下他，還是會帶他走？</p>
<p begin="11816400000t" end="11824400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">帶他走</p>
<p begin="11843200000t" end="11863200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">就算對方不希望你這樣做嗎</p>
<p begin="11871600000t" end="11886000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">強行帶他走</p>
<p begin="11886800000t" end="11897200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">因為我們逃走了</p>
<p begin="11898000000t" end="11909600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">離開孤兒院的話</p>
<p begin="11910400000t" end="11935600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">他的生命安全就未必再有保證</p>
<p begin="11952800000t" end="11990800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">而且我由始至終都想相信大家</p>
<p begin="11991600000t" end="12011200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">在經歷過我和吉爾妲的事之後</p>
<p begin="12012000000t" end="12024800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">我曾經反省</p>
<p begin="12025600000t" end="12045600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">雖然阿雷叫我去懷疑其他人</p>
<p begin="12050800000t" end="12076000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">但是就算是鬼的手下，又是內奸</p>
<p begin="12076800000t" end="12098400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">我仍然認為兄弟姐妹是善良的</p>
<p begin="12109600000t" end="12130400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">因為我們是一起成長的同伴</p>
<p begin="12131200000t" end="12148400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">就算受到阻撓、受到背叛</p>
<p begin="12149200000t" end="12164800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">被人說我天真也好</p>
<p begin="12165600000t" end="12183600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">我也一樣想相信他</p>
<p begin="12208000000t" end="12243200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">坦白說，我已猜到你會這麼說</p>
<p begin="12535200000t" end="12541600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">怎樣</p>
<p begin="12571600000t" end="12593200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">不在這裡　　不是吧</p>
<p begin="12615200000t" end="12637600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">這樣可以確定是阿唐了</p>
<p begin="12695600000t" end="12720400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">已經確定那個內奸其實就是你了</p>
<p begin="12721200000t" end="12727200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">阿雷</p>
<p begin="12910000000t" end="12934000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">(泛紅的天空)</p>
<p begin="12934800000t" end="12972000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">(如今看來如此恐怖)</p>
<p begin="12977200000t" end="12996800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">(若不知曉)</p>
<p begin="12997600000t" end="13032400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">(是否就能幸福度日)</p>
<p begin="13038400000t" end="13111200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">(又一盞溫暖的燈火悄悄熄滅)</p>
<p begin="13112000000t" end="13151200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">(不知不覺中失去了)</p>
<p begin="13152000000t" end="13211200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">(曾經誤信過　那溫柔的聲音)</p>
<p begin="13212000000t" end="13245600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">(那曾是我的一切)</p>
<p begin="13246400000t" end="13312000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">(憑著揮灑的汗水與熾熱的心)</p>
<p begin="13312800000t" end="13380000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">(我們的確抱著意志生存)</p>
<p begin="13380800000t" end="13418800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">(事到如今　還說甚麼想要你的愛)</p>
<p begin="13419600000t" end="13447200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">(動起來　不聽使喚的雙腿)</p>
<p begin="13448000000t" end="13480400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">(脫離這個牢籠)</p>
<p begin="13481200000t" end="13514000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">(抓緊明天的自由)</p>
<p begin="13514800000t" end="13546000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">(走出絕望的困境)</p>
</div>
